                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rows" style="margin-bottom: 1%; overflow: hidden;">
            <div style="float: left; width: 40%;">
                <div style="height: 300px; border: 1px solid #e6e6e6; background-color: #fff;" id="chart1">
